{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Their experimental research revealed that all three of the aforesaid layers of presentation of natural language texts might be learned by GANs.The task of handwritten signature detection was studied by Siyue et al. [89] by deploying GAN technology for the very first time.",
    "The idea of dual learning as the foundation for this, a unique network called \"SIGAN (Signature Identification GAN, SIGAN)\" was proposed.",
    "The identification threshold was set at the SIGAN-trained discriminator's losses value.",
    "It was feasible to determine the integrity of the test handwritten signature by comparing the threshold and loss value of the test image acquired by the network.",
    "The experimental data set for this study consisted of five hard pen-type signatures, some legitimate and others deliberate impersonations."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Their experimental research revealed that all three of the aforesaid layers of presentation of natural language texts might be learned by GANs.The task of handwritten signature detection was studied by Siyue et al. [89] by deploying GAN technology for the very first time."
